<br>
I looked inside while invis and was spooked by the sight of all those monkies in there.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urhionsligo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhionsligo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 56<br> <font color=#333333>(8/3/01 12:27:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=288.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/starofdavid.gif width="36" height="38"></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Can a 52 mage solo the Holgresh?</span><hr size=1> If theyre green, you can pull them single....<br>
<br>
They are easy kills, but their nukes do hurt.  I buffed my FR to 220 and was still getting hit for full.  Best thing to do is pull them in the cave far enough so that your pet can beat them down and not agro other holgresh.  Just dont get cocky and youll be fine.<br>
<br>
Oh and on a side note, sometimes they path under the world and hit you from down there...just be weary of that.  Yes your pet will be able to defend. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center">
