<br>
The singles that wander around the area outside the cave are soloable, but unless the cave is already broken, you can run into some problems pulling the Holgresh Elder or the named from teh room without friends.  When I was there it was clear that the holgresh, even while green have a serious agro range and will attack you from about half way across the cavern.  The earth pet should be able to handle anything that it faces, but we know how we are with crowd control if there are adds.  Also, like Rhionsligo said, you can easily agro them so that you are attacked from underground and you will be unable to cast at them.  Your pet however will be able to attack but you will be stuck in support mode and will have to monitor pets health while you are being attacked.<br>
<br>
The Elder con'd blue to a 54 when I was there and once broken, you should be able to hold the cave from deep in the tunnel where it widens.<br>
<br>
Reah Kitsune'Arcanis<br>
